===Verb===
[[Category:English irregular verbs]]
{{en-verb2|'''to steal'''|'''[[steals]]'''|'''[[stole]]'''|'''[[stolen]]'''|'''[[stealing]]'''}}
#{{transitive}} To [[unlawful]]ly [[take]] an item into one's own possession.
#:''Somebody '''stole''' my wallet!''
#{{intransitive}} To move [[quiet]]ly and [[sneaky|sneakily]]
#:''When everybody was asleep, she '''stole''' down the stairs and out the door.''
